      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines a YANG data model and associated mechanisms enabling subscriber-specific subscriptions to a publisher's event streams.  Applying these elements allows a subscriber to request and receive a continuous, customized feed of publisher-generated information.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
